<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-05-28T18:24:51-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-05-28T18:24:51-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-28T18:24:51-04:00</updated><title>据报道，Refreshed Beats Pill 将增加 Find My 功能、24 小时电池续航时间和更好的音质</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;泄露的 2024 Beats Pill 红色渲染图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/cxt9fLGtFLHyrhrPirmL2Yoxf9I=/78x0:923x563/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73374757/beats_pill_2024_leaked_render.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;它的外观很熟悉，但您可以期待 2024 Beats Pill 进行许多有意义的升级。&lt;/em>; |图片：9to5Mac&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;J38JTB&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/7/24151384/heres-that-unannounced-beats- pil-speaker-again-this-time-spotted-in-an-ios-beta&quot;>;泄露的渲染&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/2/24147473 /how-ch-does-someone-get-paid-for-briefly-carrying-a-speaker-in-public&quot;>;名人目击&lt;/a>;是苹果即将在夏季推出的首款 Beats Pill 扬声器的线索自从 Pill Plus 推出以来，我们称之为“迄今为止最好的”&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2015/10/7/9467123/beats-pill-plus-speaker-apple-dre&quot;>;它于 2015 年推出&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/1/10/22876792/apple-beats-pill-plus-battery-powered-speaker-discontinued&quot;>;于 2022 年停产&lt;/a>;。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5mac.com/2024/05/28/2024-beats-pill-specs/&quot;>;来自 &lt;em>;9to5Mac&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 的报告引用了未透露姓名的消息来源，给出了有关其现代化的更多详细信息。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;a6nHIB&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem- component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Beats Solo 4 评论：双方播放&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24145150/beats-solo-4- Headphones-review&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;苹果花园的围墙正在倒塌&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24141929/apple-iphone-imessage-antitrust-dma-lock -in&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 想知道您是否因为耳鸣而听到声音&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/28/24166143/apple -study-tinnitus-research-app-preliminary-data&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Fcncwt&quot;>;报告的升级包括长达 24 小时的电池续航时间，IP67防水性、通过蓝牙 5.3 实现更快、更可靠的设备配对/切换，以及在 Apple 和 Google 网络上集成“查找我的”跟踪功能。 &lt;em>;9to5Mac&lt;/em>; 还表示，苹果计划将 Pill 的充电输出和输入端口从 USB-A 输出和 Lightning 输入更新为 USB-C。还有一个可拆卸的背带（如 &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/5/2/24147473/how-much-does-someone-get-paid-for-briefly-carrying-a-speaker-in-public&quot;>;由勒布朗·詹姆斯和丹尼尔展示...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/28/24166478/apple-beats-pill-2024-rumors-features&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/28/24166478/apple-beats-pill-2024-rumors-features" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/28/24166478/apple-beats-pill-2024-rumors-features</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-28T18:15:57-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-28T18:15:57-04:00</updated><title> NFT 集团所有者表示，Wu-Tang 最稀有的专辑即将公开播放</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;武当少林黄飞鸿专辑的图片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SDA0J33ho_88HKICrIFGF_JL-hE=/0x0:1214x809/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73374737/Screenshot_2024_05_28_at_2.16.30_PM。 0 .png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;《少林往事》，&lt;em>;图片位于其当前所有者的网站上。&lt;/em>; |图片：PleasrDAO&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zikVqn&quot;>;很少有人听过&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2014/3/26/5550260/wu- tang-clan-will-only-sell-a-sing-copy-of-their-new-album&quot;>;武当派&lt;em>;少林往事&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;的唯一副本让制药公司高管 Martin Shkreli 蒙羞的部落专辑 &l